---
title: Creamy Boursin Dip Serves 4 | with Spicy Candied Walnuts and Crispy Crostini
description: Boursin cheese gets a delicious makeover with the addition of zippy lemon zest, fresh chives and a spicy walnut topping! Served alongside are crispy crostini for dunking or spreading.

